<D>__{the day of the funeral was almost springlike. the snowline crossed new hampshire west to east, retreating northward to concord where it melted by midmorning.}
<A>__{rev. doughty finishes. the mourners exchange farewells. wade looks at lillian. margie and rolfe, escorting wade's father, let him be. he walks over, hugs jill.}
